    <DisplayName>Archive Azure DevOps projects and data   </DisplayName>
    <Description xml:space="preserve"> Secure, enterprise-grade archiving of legacy, inactive Azure DevOps data into a structured database accessible from ALM-like read-only UI for compliance, audits, and long-term retention.</Description>
