    <Categories>Azure Boards</Categories>
    <Tags>Archiving Data,Archive Azure DevOps data,ALM interface,Secure data,Store data,Inactive data,Compliance,Scale,Full Context,Azure DevOps Server Data,Data Archive,Data storage,Audit ready,Secure Api,No code,Read only UI,Historical Data,Cost reduction,Long-term data retention,Microsoft partner,__DoNotDownload</Tags>
